item.title: Anyone have a list of commands?
item.dc:creator: @heatrn11 heatrn11
item.description:
@heatrn11 wrote:

::giveadmin
::donator (username)
::kick
::hide
::npc (number) - spawns that NPC
::pnpc (number) Turns your character into that NPC
::ipban
::sz - teleports you to staff-zone
::ticket if someone requires help, a message will appear on the chatbox
::staffmeeting
::kick
::dz[/quote]
Why do you assume those are the commands, you don’t even know the revision or base.
